Another glow map, its quite small because i just got an idea, decided to make it, made it all yesterday so havent put a lot of time into it, but i feel like i managed to make what i pictured in my head before i had even opened hammer. 

Hope you like it, i think the map should be around 50 seconds after play testing it.

Also thanks to Asko for providing a video of the map from our play testing :)
